{
  "id": "select_by_expression_export@1",
  "version": "1.0",
  "env_id": "qgis_env@0.1",
  "description": "A demographic analyst needs to extract the world's mega-cities from the Natural Earth Populated Places dataset located at '/home/ga/GIS_Data/ne_110m_populated_places_simple/ne_110m_populated_places_simple.shp'. Filter the dataset to include only features where the 'pop_max' attribute is greater than 10,000,000. Export these selected features to '/home/ga/GIS_Data/exports/major_megacities.geojson' in GeoJSON format.",
